{"tid":1657432,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"眾志前副主席袁嘉蔚獲批入閘參選區議會","createTime":"2019-10-16T05:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T11:40:10.000Z","uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"372834eaa1d97b32b6d5aa1e7fc6c8dc81d775c0","tid":1657432,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】區議會選舉提名期明日結束，香港眾志前副主席袁嘉蔚參選資格獲確認。<br />\n<br />\n袁嘉蔚在社交網站上載通知書，選舉主任確認她參選南區田灣選區的資格，其間未曾向她查詢。同區已報名參選的是尋求連任的陳富明，他報稱獨立。<br />\n<br />\n另外，參選九龍城樂民選區的林正軒亦獲確認參選資格，他提交的政綱寫明「光復香港，時代革命」，選舉主任未曾向他查詢，同區已報名的是現任區議員楊永杰。"},{"pid":"7802ba7cfe317de03eee19ff481f0a0d0596bfdc","tid":1657432,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f946220832e43685e9909cdac626c2138684bfcb","tid":1657432,"uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T11:40:10.000Z","msg":"[和理Post] 過嚟問下啲區議員候選人喇喂<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=81158a6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6</a><br />\n<br />\n連登Post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1666510\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1666510</a>"}]}